	<entry>
		<title type="html"><![CDATA[Re: Does this Dictionary overrides Sanskrit Grammar?]]></title>
		<link rel="alternate" href="http://spokensanskrit.de/board/forum/viewtopic.php?pid=1995#p1995"/>
		<content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>In any case, it is not available on search of Vedic literature as given Bloomfield or in any text available in DCS, in the causative form. Unless he has given the precise reference, it is difficult to believe it is found in Rigveda or any other texts for that matter.</p>]]></content>
		<author>
			<name><![CDATA[hnbhat]]></name>
			<uri>http://spokensanskrit.de/board/forum/profile.php?id=747</uri>
		</author>
